title: War of the Roses: He's Been Staying at His Ex's House
description: Amanda is concerned there's something going on with her boyfriend and his ex.  He has kids with her and he's been telling Amanda he's just trying to spend more time with them but now he's slept at his ex's a couple times and Amanda feels like something more is going on then him just wanting to be with his kids.
